The CognitiveQG expert annotations in this directory — reasoning-trace and
Socratic-question annotations, the two-annotator inter-annotator files, and the
derived consistency/2x2 labels — are licensed under the Creative Commons
Attribution 4.0 International License (CC BY 4.0).

