-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
NOTE ON SOURCE ARGUMENTS
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
The underlying argument texts are drawn from the FOCUS benchmark and are NOT
redistributed here: the `argument` field in every data file is intentionally
left blank. Obtain the source arguments from the FOCUS release and re-join them
to these annotations via the `argumentIndex` field. FOCUS source arguments
remain governed by FOCUS's own terms of use.
